235
00:44:09,520 --> 00:44:13,440
sir...
yes yes yes, you will be decorated with the medal of honor

236
00:44:13,840 --> 00:44:19,080
I've never in my career lost a fight

237
00:44:19,640 --> 00:44:22,280
Gentlemen, I will repeat once in perfect to you

238
00:44:22,600 --> 00:44:25,560
We will not be in fight with Muktar or 200 of his men here or 50 of his men there

239
00:44:26,000 --> 00:44:29,200
we are fighting a population

240
00:44:32,520 --> 00:44:36,240
I am therefore taking the first 3 final steps

241
00:44:36,520 --> 00:44:39,720
straight to eliminate rebellion in this economy

242
00:44:41,360 --> 00:44:44,320
Its really quite simple and really should have been thought out before

243
00:44:44,800 --> 00:44:48,280
I propose to concentrate on the Beduins

244
00:44:48,560 --> 00:44:50,200
concentrate them?

245
