Yes, put them in a high walled camps and keep them there until we find prudent and safe to release them

246
00:44:57,440 --> 00:45:01,360
No need of any pity for them
They have brought this upon themselves

247
00:45:02,720 --> 00:45:07,080
We will fill their wells, we will burn their fuels,

248
00:45:07,400 --> 00:45:10,200
we will destroy their trees
we will turn their land brown

249
00:45:10,240 --> 00:45:12,800
Now, if they cannot live with it, they'll leave it

250
00:45:14,280 --> 00:45:18,440
And.. if we meet the resistance?
you answer it prompty with your own punishment for rebellion

251
00:45:18,800 --> 00:45:19,760
Thats the message

252
00:45:48,560 --> 00:45:51,560
Turn around

253
00:45:53,400 --> 00:45:57,320
As mutinists and rebels,
you will be decimated

254
00:46:14,160 --> 00:46:17,160
