468
01:26:48,520 --> 01:26:51,040
Hilgariani's coming up the Merch Road

469
01:26:51,360 --> 01:26:54,840
How many?
Three
They are flying white flags

470
01:26:55,360 --> 01:26:57,480
Let them in

471
01:26:59,880 --> 01:27:01,880
We will finish later

472
01:27:27,640 --> 01:27:30,600
Sheriff Hilgariani

473
01:27:32,800 --> 01:27:35,600
To come through, we have to use the Italian cars

474
01:27:36,000 --> 01:27:41,800
you sound and comfortable?
We want to talk to you alone

475
01:27:42,400 --> 01:27:44,880
