476
01:27:45,160 --> 01:27:48,200
Then, it is not to be said to me

477
01:27:49,440 --> 01:27:53,880
Omar, why do you not surrender?
We've obtained the best terms you can from the Italians

478
01:27:56,720 --> 01:27:59,880
Mohamed will re-direct a safe conduct out of the country

479
01:27:59,920 --> 01:28:03,640
safe conduct?
Where to?
Egypt

480
01:28:03,920 --> 01:28:06,840
To Egypt... To hide with his brother

481
01:28:07,320 --> 01:28:11,320
