02:22:35,440 --> 02:22:37,320
What age are you?

743
02:22:39,480 --> 02:22:41,800
73

744
02:22:42,920 --> 02:22:46,600
Are you the head of the forces in Libia fighting against Italy?

745
02:22:49,560 --> 02:22:51,160
Yes, I am

746
02:22:54,680 --> 02:22:58,080
Have you taken part in attacks on Italian Soldiers?

747
02:22:59,400 --> 02:23:01,520
Yes, I have

748
02:23:02,400 --> 02:23:06,520
For how long, have you taken part in attacks on Italian Soldiers?

749
02:23:08,960 --> 02:23:10,800
20 years

750
02:23:11,440 --> 02:23:13,680
How many attacks?

751
02:23:15,520 --> 02:23:20,320
No... I... I couldn't remember the number

752
02:23:22,440 --> 02:23:25,280
Ordering the torturing and murdering of Italian Prisoners?

753
02:23:25,880 --> 02:23:27,200
I did not

754
02:23:27,560 --> 02:23:29,040
Never

755
02:23:29,040 --> 02:23:31,720
You were captured with arms in your hands

756
02:23:32,400 --> 02:23:34,760
Yes, I was

757
02:23:56,120 --> 02:23:58,840
The enemy was insulted

758
02:23:59,640 --> 02:24:02,680
In the field, I would reason it

759
02:24:04,120 --> 02:24:08,640
... but here

760
02:24:08,760 --> 02:24:09,640
I am obliged to

761
02:24:09,840 --> 02:24:11,840
I am appointed to defend him

762
02:24:15,280 --> 02:24:17,320
You are an old man

763
02:24:19,600 --> 02:24:22,680
older, than all of us here

764
02:24:23,080 --> 02:24:26,840
and I will not abuse you with too many questions

765
02:24:28,400 --> 02:24:31,880
Did you ever submit to the Italian Authority?

766
02:24:32,200 --> 02:24:34,600
I did not

767
02:24:35,400 --> 02:24:39,680
Did you ever receive money or other subsidy from the Italian Government?

768
02:24:40,240 --> 02:24:44,720
as a condition of good behaviour?

769
02:24:46,680 --> 02:24:48,920
I did not

770
02:24:49,880 --> 02:24:51,160
Never

771
02:24:51,840 --> 02:24:53,080
I declare

772
02:24:53,960 --> 02:24:58,400
that Omar Muktar never submitted to us

773
02:24:58,760 --> 02:25:01,400
never took subsity from us

774
02:25:01,560 --> 02:25:06,200
never recognize our right to rule in this colony

775
02:25:06,760 --> 02:25:12,960
He cannot therefore,
illogic or justice betrayed by us as a rebel

776
02:25:13,600 --> 02:25:19,960
When we captured Omar Muktar,
after 20 years of battles

777
02:25:20,360 --> 02:25:26,880
we are morally obliged to do with him
as a prisoner of war

778
02:25:37,320 --> 02:25:40,200
Quiet... Silence in Court

779
02:25:46,120 --> 02:25:54,200
Captain Antono, you were ordered to defend this rebel against the charge of treason

780
02:25:55,320 --> 02:26:00,800
You have over-stepped your orders

781
02:26:08,400 --> 02:26:11,320
The sentence on you Omar Muktar

782
02:26:12,320 --> 02:26:13,720
is that by HANGING

783
02:26:14,000 --> 02:26:15,960
in public

784
02:26:17,320 --> 02:26:20,320
at the dawn of Sadook at 7 O'clock tomorrow

785
02:26:20,800 --> 02:26:24,760
the 16th of September, 1931

786
02:26:26,400 --> 02:26:32,160
You denign of the Fascist Era

787
02:26:32,960 --> 02:26:38,000
From God we come
and unto God, we shall return

788
02:27:33,200 --> 02:27:36,800
In the name of the Government of the Republic of Italian Selanaica

789
02:27:37,360 --> 02:27:40,000
we execute this sentence

790
02:27:40,920 --> 02:27:43,080
as agreed by the military tribunal Thengiazi

791
02:27:43,280 --> 02:27:47,600
on the 15th day of September 1931
year 9 of the Fascist Theorm

792
02:27:48,320 --> 02:27:53,040
Omar Muktar, you have been found guilty of high treason
both morally and materially

793
02:27:53,440 --> 02:27:59,800
on staging the rebellion against the Italian Government of this Colony

794
02:28:01,040 --> 02:28:07,040
Your sentence passed by the Court
thereby hanging in a public place

795
02:28:07,840 --> 02:28:09,520
will now be carried out

796
02:30:30,040 --> 02:30:35,920
making Nasiyath
to be hanged by the hands of the enemies

797
02:31:40,040 --> 02:31:41,720
Untie him

